WEBVTT

00:05:58.443 --> 00:06:01.475
When we invest in the redemptive
value of relevancy,

00:06:01.499 --> 00:06:05.891
we can render a return of both
personal responsibility and healing.

00:06:06.304 --> 00:06:08.548
That's the people work I care about,

00:06:08.572 --> 00:06:10.004
because people work.

00:06:11.313 --> 00:06:15.241
Family, I'm asking you
to do the hard work,

00:06:15.265 --> 00:06:16.713
the difficult work,

00:06:16.737 --> 00:06:19.672
the churning work of bestowing
undeserved kindness

00:06:19.696 --> 00:06:22.143
upon those who we can relegate as garbage,

00:06:22.167 --> 00:06:24.335
who we can disregard and discard easily.

00:06:25.023 --> 00:06:26.349
I'm asking myself.

00:06:27.510 --> 00:06:29.430
Over the past two months,

00:06:29.454 --> 00:06:31.548
I've lost two friends to gun violence,